<plot>A feminine comedy about a happy family that breaks down when Sonny falls in with the wrong crowd and starts behaving strangely. The source of his problem is revealed when the Lad-About-Town, the Connoisseur, the Stud and the Pseudo-Intellectual attend Mommy's eclectic birthday party. She discovers they're spreading Young Man's Disease and Sonny has caught it. What's a mother to do? Can she save her son from this dreaded disease? Or must she learn to live and let live with obnoxious young men roaming the earth?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?188931</url></doc>
